ause%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20taught%20this%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20should%20repeat%20it%20with%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20is%20watching%20a%20screen%2C%20they%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20anything%20around%20them.%20That%20is%20the%20core%20issue%20which%20leads%20to%20many%20mental%20health%20problems.%20To%20prevent%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20involve%20children%20in%20a%20daily%20routine%20doing%20household%20chores%2C%20take%20them%20outside%2C%20and%20build%20a%20community%20of%20friends%20for%20them%20to%20play%20with.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20keep%20children%20involved%20in%20purposeful%20work%20which%20also%20fosters%20empathy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEmotions%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20replaced%20with%20mobile%20phones%20or%20screens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20parents%2C%20Harpreet%20offers%20a%20few%20basic%20pieces%20of%20advice%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362808%5C%2