157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-2-1724393507-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-2-1724393507-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-2-1724393507-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkash%20with%20his%20younger%20sister.%20On%20the%20right%20are%20his%20cousin%20and%20sister-in-law%20who%20took%20him%20in.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%E2%80%99s%20goals%20were%20never%20deterred%20by%20his%20cousin%E2%80%99s%20meagre%20resources.%20He%20encouraged%20him%20to%20strive%20high%20and%20follow%20his%20aspirations.%20He%20eventually%20pursued%20mechanical%20engineering%20from%20a%20local%20college%20in%20Vadodara%20where%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20naturally%20inclined%20to%20social%20work%20and%20was%20exploring%20ways%20in%20which%20I%20could%20contribute%20to%20the%20community%20directly.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20from%20my%20college%20friends.%20When%20I%20searched%20more%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20this%20work%20can%20not%20only%20help%20me%20engage%20with%20the%20community%20directly%20but%20also%20help%20me%20grow%20personally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20delved%20into%20the%20world%20of%20competitive%20exams%20after%20his%20graduation%20in%202018%2C%20Akash%20encountered%20further%20hurdles%3B%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20his%20Gujarati-medium%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20quality%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-me