0holds%20true.%20But%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20he%20cautions.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20make%20mistakes%20and%20you%20will%20learn%20from%20them%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20you%20might%20not%20get%20it%20right.%20But%20with%20each%20season%2C%20you%20will%20learn%20to%20refine%20your%20techniques%20and%20to%20read%20your%20plants%20and%20understand%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20making%20inferences%20on%20plant%20health%20when%20he%20begins%20spotting%20signs%20of%20disease%20cropping%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20that%20I%20have%20sent%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20plant%20to%20the%20agricultural%20development%20officer%20explaining%20the%20symptoms.%20They%20responded%20saying%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20fungal%20infection%20and%20that%20I%20should%20resort%20to%20a%20particular%20chemical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20like%20these%2C%20when%20Deka%20responds%20by%20saying%20he%20does%20not%20use%20chemicals%20on%20his%20plants%2C%20the%20line%20remains%20silent%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20This%20journey%20of%20odds%20would%20deter%20him%20you%E2%80%99d%20think.%20But%20it%20only%20makes%20him%20more%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500-plus%20trees%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20Medini%20Homestay%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Indian%20olive%2C%20guava%2C%20mango%2C%20papaya%2C%20and%20banana%20%E2%80%94%20sway%20in%20the%20breeze%2C%20almost%20bowing%20down%20to%20him%20in%20thanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20passion%20project%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20wood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20around%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20filled%20with%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20glistening%20wat